  "detailed_description": "<i>Through me you pass into the city of woe<br>                                                                                                                                                                                         Through me you pass into eternal pain<br>                                                                                                                                                                                         Through me among the people lost for aye.</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Dante Alighieri, The Divine Comedy: Hell,CantoIII</h2><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1058290/extras/mortido_\u043f\u043b\u0430\u0448\u043a\u0430_1_en.png?t=1563801373\" ><br>Mortido is an action-adventure game, the story about sinful soul in search of redemption. <br>The main purpose of the game is to redeem yourself by saving souls of people whose lives you ones ruined.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1058290/extras/ezgif-5-cfde68f7ddb9.gif?t=1563801373\" ><br><br>Main character appears in the underworld after his own death with a great desire to repair the damage he has caused and that gives his soul incredible strength. <br>In the course of the game, a player needs to fight through a number of different worlds, face various monsters created by hate and finally help broken souls to reach a better place.<br>Player learns a story about these people before their death through multiple items, figures out how they are connected and why they ended up in such dark and hopeless world.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1058290/extras/ezgif-5-8db87627a194.gif?t=1563801373\" ><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/1058290/extras/mortido_\u043f\u043b\u0430\u0448\u043a\u0430_2_en.png?t=1563801373\" ><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Gloomy, but atmospheric setting.<br></li><li>Mysterious masked anti-hero.<br></li><li>Surrealism and nightmares are your new friends.<br></li><li>Charon and other mythological characters are waiting to \u201cmingle\u201d with you.<br></li><li>A fascinating story about travelling to personal hell and back.</li></ul>",
